l l l.
Interface	Attribute	Value
T{
.BR towctrans ()
T}	Thread safety	MT-Safe
.TE
.SH CONFORMING TO
POSIX.1-2001, POSIX.1-2008, C99.
.SH NOTES
The behavior of
.BR towctrans ()
depends on the
.B LC_CTYPE
category of the
current locale.
